data.description: Welcome to your dream home on the prestigious Players Club Deer Creek Golf Course! Nestled at hole 13, this magnificent 1.5-story residence boasts an incredible blend of luxury, convenience, and breathtaking views. You'll be awestruck by the stunning 2 story great room with curved staircase.The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream w/ JennAir Appliances, 2 ovens & pot filler.  Upstairs, enjoy the multipurpose loft room along with 3 generous-sized bedrooms.  The walkout lower level is a blank canvas to finish as you please. Other perks: tankless water heater, central vac, water softener, sprinkler system, & fully fenced yard. An oasis of comfort and luxury, offering the perfect balance of upscale living and the beauty of a golf course community. Don't miss the opportunity to call this stunning house your new home.  Schedule a showing today and experience the lifestyle that awaits you in this remarkable property.
